{"tid":538145,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今早打破了水杯 你問我答","createTime":"2018-01-23T11:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T16:23:22.000Z","uid":97431,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e1bcf83df2050195394dde7926c785422ab20e50","tid":538145,"uid":97431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:05:54.000Z","msg":"今天不小心把心愛的水杯打碎了　事後我用了十五分鐘去細心欣賞　發現打碎了的玻璃碎　竟然比起平日那個形態更美　然後我再用了十分鐘去打掃地方　再為其拍照　這短短的三十分鐘　算是今天我思緒最安穩的時間　打碎了的水杯　是我今天看過最美好的東西　而那水杯著地的那一聲　是聽過最美好的聲音　原來人生覺得最爛的事情　也未必是最糟　因為最糟的　可能一直就在眼前而未曾發現　又或者根本就是自己　我想我找到了答案<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/190545_3d3cd2676723f0f73df526933fe7107b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F190545_3d3cd2676723f0f73df526933fe7107b.png&h=59482933&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9ab1496b17d3f6316de22d4f9265f99ed0f17ca","tid":538145,"uid":46435,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:10:33.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"f7c13580abded4eeeb844a6d336ddd54373c6d80","tid":538145,"uid":97431,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f9ab1496b17d3f6316de22d4f9265f99ed0f17ca","tid":538145,"uid":46435,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:10:33.000Z","msg":"閱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:13:12.000Z","msg":"你不覺得很有意義嗎"},{"pid":"8d7117f06519c1d6a4607e48865e6e11b8d5c59c","tid":538145,"uid":30573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:15:08.000Z","msg":"你幾時會入返去精靈球？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad09cfb0e699362a743afbe8d1ffdfa2266f7f9","tid":538145,"uid":11760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:15:25.000Z","msg":"你係林明貞定周柏豪？"},{"pid":"a1d1b9c31406f1f3681f4cd912d90d40e469a996","tid":538145,"uid":97431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d7117f06519c1d6a4607e48865e6e11b8d5c59c","tid":538145,"uid":30573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s